'''柳京飯店'''（{{kor|名=北|k=류경호텔|hj=柳京호텔|rm=Ryugyŏng Hotel}}）是位於[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|北韓]]首都[[平壤市|平壤]]一座高度{{convert|330|m|ft}}的[[金字塔|金字塔]]狀摩天大樓，设计层数105层<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.orientalarchitecture.com/koreanorth/pyongyang/105building.php |title=105 Building, Pyongyang, Korea, North |publisher=Asian Historical Architecture |access-date=2010-02-11 |archive-date=2010-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100216164138/http://www.orientalarchitecture.com/koreanorth/pyongyang/105building.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其名稱“[[柳树|柳]]京”為平壤的古名之一<ref>{{cite book |last=Funabashi |first=Yoichi |title=The Peninsula Question: A Chronicle of the Second Northern Korean Nuclear Crisis |url=https://archive.org/details/peninsulaquestio00funa |publisher=Brookings Institution Press |location=Washington, DC |year=2007 |page=[https://archive.org/details/peninsulaquestio00funa/page/n64 50] |isbn=978-0-8157-3010-1}}</ref>。柳京飯店又因其樓層數而有“'''105大樓'''”的別稱<ref name=Emporis/>。柳京飯店是一座{{link-en|混合用途發展|Mixed-use development}}的[[摩天大楼|摩天大楼]]，其中包含一个约3000间客房的酒店<ref name="doom"/>。

柳京飯店於1987年動工，惟後來因[[苏联解体|苏联解体]]導致的[[苦难的行军|經濟危機]]而於1992年停工。1992年後，柳京飯店建築封頂，但未安裝窗戶與內部配件。柳京飯店於2008年復工，而外牆於2011年完工。柳京飯店曾多次預計启用而未果，例如预计2012年[[金日成|金日成]]100歲冥誕時启用，随后2013年宣告柳京飯店局部啓用，但中途取消<ref name="Berg2016">{{cite web |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/02/14/north-korea-s-best-building-is-empty-the-mystery-of-the-ryugyong-hotel.html |title=North Korea's Best Building Is Empty: The Mystery of the Ryugyong Hotel |work=The Daily Beast |date=2016-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160214202302/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/02/14/north-korea-s-best-building-is-empty-the-mystery-of-the-ryugyong-hotel.html |archive-date=2016-02-14 |url-status=live |first=Nate |last=Berg }}</ref>，最终在2016年完工<ref name="completion"/>，並在翌年7月27日正式啓用<ref name="opening">{{cite news|author=馬麗|title=歷經三代 北韓最高「厄運酒店」悄悄開張|date=2017-08-01|url=https://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n221968/%E6%AD%B7%E7%B6%93%E4%B8%89%E4%BB%A3-%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%84%E9%81%8B%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E9%96%8B%E5%BC%B5.html|accessdate=2022-03-17|agency=[[大纪元时报|大纪元时报]]|archive-date=2022-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220322024549/https://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n221968/%E6%AD%B7%E7%B6%93%E4%B8%89%E4%BB%A3-%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%84%E9%81%8B%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E9%96%8B%E5%BC%B5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。柳京飯店开业后一側外牆於2018年安裝[[发光二极管显示器|LED螢幕]]，用於播放[[朝鲜政治宣传|政治宣傳]]動畫與電影<ref>{{cite news |title=Ryugyong, the world's tallest empty hotel, dazzles North Korean capital skyline with propaganda light shows |work=South China Morning Post |date=2018-12-30 |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/east-asia/article/2180004/ryugyong-worlds-tallest-empty-hotel-dazzles-north-korean-capital |accessdate=2022-03-14 |archive-date=2021-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210809172506/https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/east-asia/article/2180004/ryugyong-worlds-tallest-empty-hotel-dazzles-north-korean-capital |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==建築==
柳京飯店高{{Convert|330|m|ft}}<ref>{{cite news |title=North Korea's 'Hotel of Doom' to open 24 years after construction: by numbers |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=2011-10-10 |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/northkorea/8817892/North-Koreas-Hotel-of-Doom-to-open-24-years-after-construction-by-numbers.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111075207/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/northkorea/8817892/North-Koreas-Hotel-of-Doom-to-open-24-years-after-construction-by-numbers.html |archive-date=2021-01-11 |url-status=no |accessdate=2022-03-14 }}{{cbignore}}</ref>，使之成為平壤[[天際線|天際線]]至為突出的部分，以及[[朝鮮摩天大樓與結構物列表|北韓境內最高的建築物]]<ref>{{Cite web|last=Lakritz|first=Talia|title=North Korea's tallest building is an abandoned hotel that has never hosted a single guest – take a closer look at the 'Hotel of Doom'|url=https://www.insider.com/abandoned-hotel-north-korea-ryugyong-photos-2019-11|access-date=2020-10-23|website=Insider|archive-date=2022-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314120143/https://www.insider.com/abandoned-hotel-north-korea-ryugyong-photos-2019-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。柳京飯店原定於1992年金日成80歲壽辰時完工<ref>{{cite book|last=Hwang|first=Kyung Moon|title=A History of Korea|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ITy7DQAAQBAJ&pg=PT316|edition=2nd|year=2016|publisher=Palgrave Macmillan|location=Basingstoke|isbn=978-1-137-57358-2|page=316|access-date=2022-03-14|archive-date=2022-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314120146/https://books.google.com/books?id=ITy7DQAAQBAJ&pg=PT316|dead-url=no}}</ref>，如成事，柳京飯店將成為當時[[世界最高酒店列表|世界最高的酒店]]<ref>{{Cite web|author=Jacopo Prisco|title=Ryugyong Hotel: The story of North Korea's 'Hotel of Doom'|url=https://www.cnn.com/style/article/ryugyong-hotel-architecture-origins/index.html|access-date=2020-10-23|website=CNN|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304001805/https://www.cnn.com/style/article/ryugyong-hotel-architecture-origins/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。柳京飯店在[[高银金融117|高银金融117]]封頂前是世界最高的[[爛尾建築|爛尾建築]]<ref>{{cite web |first=Jacopo |last=Prisco |title=Ryugyong Hotel: The story of North Korea's 'Hotel of Doom' |url=https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/ryugyong-hotel-architecture-origins/index.html |publisher=CNN |date=2019-08-10 |access-date=2022-01-10 |quote=Still closed to this day, the Ryugyong Hotel is the world's tallest unoccupied building. |archive-date=2022-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206082221/https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/ryugyong-hotel-architecture-origins/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Tallest building unoccupied">{{cite web |author1=Guinness World Records |author-link1=Guinness World Records |title=Tallest building unoccupied |url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/tallest-building-unoccupied |website=Guinness World Records |publisher=Guinness World Records |access-date=2022-01-10 |quote=Tallest building unoccupied |archive-date=2022-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107233342/https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/tallest-building-unoccupied |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

柳京飯店分為三翼，各翼長{{Convert|100|m|ft}}、闊{{Convert|18|m|ft}}，與地面保持75度的傾角<ref name="Esquire"/>，並於頂部聚成一點。柳京飯店的頂部為{{Convert|40|m|ft}}闊的截[[圆锥|錐]]，內有8層預定旋轉樓層，上有6層固定樓層。柳京飯店原預期將設有5所[[旋轉餐廳|旋轉餐廳]]，以及{{nts|3000}}或{{nts|7665}}間客房<ref name="revolving">{{cite book |last=Randl |first=Chad |title=Revolving Architecture: A History of Buildings That Rotate, Swivel, and Pivot |publisher=Princeton Architectural Press |location=New York |year=2008 |page=[https://archive.org/details/revolvingarchite00rand/page/133 133] |isbn=978-1-56898-681-4 |url=https://archive.org/details/revolvingarchite00rand/page/133 }}</ref><ref name="Quinones2003">{{cite book |last1=Quinones |first1=C. Kenneth |first2=Joseph |last2=Taggert |title=The Complete Idiot's Guide to Understanding North Korea |publisher=Alpha Books |location=Indianapolis |year=2003 |series=Complete Idiot's Guides |page=183 |chapter=The Economy: Supporting the Military |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uWOSvlp9jwMC&pg=PA183 |isbn=978-1-59257-169-7 |lccn=2003113809 |oclc=54510387 |ol=8867625M |access-date=2022-03-14 |archive-date=2020-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200506224154/https://books.google.com/books?id=uWOSvlp9jwMC&pg=PA183 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據2009年{{link-en|奧斯康建設|Orascom Construction|奧斯康集團}}的{{link-en|哈立德·比沙拉|Khaled Bichara}}的説法，柳京飯店將不會僅作為酒店，而會成為混合用途發展大樓，其中將設有旋轉餐廳與“酒店住宿、公寓與商務設施的混合體”<ref name="doom"/>。

==建造==
===開工===
北韓建造大型酒店的計劃據傳是[[冷战|冷战]]背景下對1986年由[[大韩民国|南韓]]公司{{link-en|雙龍集團|SsangYong Group}}興建的[[史丹福瑞士酒店|史丹福瑞士酒店]]完工的回應<ref name="oversight"/>。北韓領導層將柳京飯店項目設想為西方投資者進入北韓市場的渠道<ref name="oversight"/>。北韓當局為此成立“柳京飯店投資與管理”公司，並預期能吸引2.3億美元的外國投資<ref name="oversight"/>。北韓政府的代表承諾會放鬆監管力度，並容許“外國投資者經營[[賭場|賭場]]、[[夜總會|夜總會]]或{{link-ja|接待飲食店|ラウンジ (接待飲食店)}}”<ref name="oversight">{{cite journal |last=Ngor |first=Oh Kwee |date=1990-06-09 |title=Western decadence hits N. Korea |journal=Japan Economic Journal |page=12}}</ref>。北韓建築公司白頭山建築研究院（{{lang|ko|백두산건축연구원}}）於1987年開始興建一座金字塔狀的酒店大樓<ref name=IFES>{{cite web |url=http://ifes.kyungnam.ac.kr/eng/m05/s10/content.asp?nkbriefNO=207&GoP=1 |title=Orascom and DPRK to Complete Ryugyong Hotel Construction |publisher=The Institute for Far Eastern Studies |date=2008-05-20 |access-date=2010-02-09 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090703133311/http://ifes.kyungnam.ac.kr/eng/m05/s10/content.asp?nkbriefNO=207&GoP=1 |archive-date=2009-07-03 }}</ref><ref name="almanac">{{cite book |title=Almanac of Architecture & Design |url=https://archive.org/details/almanacofarchite0007unse |editor1=Cramer, James P. |editor2=Jennifer Evans Yankopolus |publisher=Greenway Publications |location=Atlanta |year=2006 |edition=7th |page=[https://archive.org/details/almanacofarchite0007unse/page/368 368] |isbn=0-9755654-2-7}}</ref>。

柳京飯店原定於1992年時任[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國主席|國家主席]]金日成80歲壽辰時開業，惟因建築方法與材料等問題使完工日期延誤<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/northkorea/6337040/North-Korean-hotel-dubbed-the-worst-building-in-the-world-may-finally-be-finished.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111075155/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/northkorea/6337040/North-Korean-hotel-dubbed-the-worst-building-in-the-world-may-finally-be-finished.html |archive-date=2021-01-11 |url-status=no |title=North Korean hotel dubbed the 'worst building in the world' may finally be finished |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date=2009-10-16 |access-date=2010-08-25 }}{{cbignore}}</ref>。如柳京飯店如期開業，柳京飯店將超越史丹福瑞士酒店成為當時世界最高的酒店<ref name="ABC">{{cite news |first=Dan |last=Beckmann |title=Pyongyang: Home to the Tallest Hotel in the World That Could, but Will Never Be |url=https://abcnews.go.com/print?id=2590901 |publisher=ABC News |date=2006-10-23 |access-date=2009-07-05 |archive-date=2021-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319110841/https://abcnews.go.com/print?id=2590901 |dead-url=no }}</ref>與[[摩天大樓列表|世界第七高樓]]<ref name=Emporis/>。

===停工===
柳京飯店大樓於1992年達到其完整的建築高度後<ref name=Emporis>{{cite web |url=http://www.emporis.com/buildings/130967/ryugyong-hotel-pyongyang-north-korea |title=Ryugyong Hotel |access-date=2010-02-09 |work=Emporis |archive-date=2022-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220216031306/https://www.emporis.com/buildings/130967/ryugyong-hotel-pyongyang-north-korea |dead-url=no }}</ref>因蘇聯解體導致的經濟危機而停工<ref name="doom"/>。[[日本報紙|日本報章]]估計柳京飯店造價7.5億美元<ref name="cost">{{cite journal |title=North Korea builds record-height hotel |date=1990-11-15 |journal=Engineering News-Record |page=41}}</ref>，約為北韓[[国内生产总值|国内生产总值]]的2%<ref name="Esquire"/>。柳京飯店在此後逾10年空置，未安裝任何窗戶、固定裝置或配件，如同巨大的[[混凝土|混凝土]]外殼<ref name=Emporis/>。一台生鏽的建築起重機仍留在大樓頂部，[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]形容柳京飯店“使人想起[[極權主義|極權主義]]政權未竟的野心”<ref name=doom/><ref name="Kirk2008">{{cite news |last=Kirk |first=Donald |publication-date=17 October 2008 |title=Grand Illusion |periodical=Forbes |url=https://www.forbes.com/global/2008/1027/059.html |access-date=2009-07-05 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225112051/http://www.forbes.com/global/2008/1027/059.html |archive-date=2015-12-25 }}</ref>。根據馬庫斯·諾蘭（{{lang|en|Marcus Noland}}）的説法，{{link-en|朝鮮半島歐洲商會|European Chamber of Commerce in Korea (ECCK)}}於1990年代後期對柳京飯店大樓進行檢查，並得出大樓無法修復的結論<ref>{{cite book |last=Noland |first=Marcus |title=Avoiding the Apocalypse: The Future of the Two Koreas |publisher=Institute for International Economics |location=Washington, DC |year=2000 |page=[https://archive.org/details/avoidingapocalyp00nola_0/page/82 82] |isbn=0-88132-278-4 |url=https://archive.org/details/avoidingapocalyp00nola_0/page/82 }}</ref>。柳京飯店大樓的混凝土質量與[[電梯|電梯]]井定位遭受質疑，惟部分消息人士稱相關問題“不實”<ref name=doom/><ref name="Quinones2003"/>。

[[ABC新聞|ABC新聞]]於其2006年的報導對北韓是否有充足的[[原材料|原材料]]與能源進行如此浩大的工程表示質疑<ref name="ABC"/>。有北韓政府官員於2008年向《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》透露柳京飯店建造工程“因資金不足”而未能完成<ref name="boom">{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/sep/27/world/fg-boom27 |title=North Korea in the midst of mysterious building boom |date=2008-09-27 |work=Los Angeles Times |access-date=2008-12-14 |first=Barbara |last=Demick |archive-date=2016-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822072652/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/sep/27/world/fg-boom27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

雖然在柳京飯店興建初期，北韓郵票上出現了酒店完工後的模擬圖像，但[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国政府|北韓政府]]仍於停工期間忽略佔據平壤天際線的柳京飯店的存在。北韓政府對官方照片[[修飾照片|進行篡改]]，以將爛尾的柳京飯店自平壤的天際線中移除，並不再在印刷本平壤地圖上顯示柳京飯店。<ref name="ABC"/><ref name=boom/><ref name=doom/>

柳京飯店的停工、有關其各種問題的傳聞與有關其未來的謎團使外國媒體稱之為“世界最差建築物”<ref name="Esquire">{{cite web |publication-date=28 January 2008 |title=The Worst Building in the History of Mankind |periodical=Esquire |url=http://www.esquire.com/news-politics/a4184/hotel-of-doom-012808/ |access-date=2009-07-05 |first=Eva |last=Hagberg |date=2008-01-28 |archive-date=2021-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210714141049/https://www.esquire.com/news-politics/a4184/hotel-of-doom-012808/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Independent">{{cite news |last=Herskovitz |first=Jon |publication-date=18 July 2008 |title=North Koreans revamp 'world's worst building' |work=The Independent |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-koreans-revamp-worlds-worst-building-870858.html |access-date=2009-07-05 |location=London |archive-date=2012-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120203021113/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-koreans-revamp-worlds-worst-building-870858.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、“厄運酒店”與“幽靈酒店”<ref name="doom">{{cite news |title=Will 'Hotel of Doom' ever be finished? |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/8306697.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=2009-10-15 |access-date=2009-10-13 |archive-date=2009-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091015024340/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/8306697.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===復工===
[[File:2008_-_Top_of_the_Ryugyong_Hotel,_Pyongyang_(filter_enhanced).jpg|thumb]]
2008年4月，埃及建築公司奧斯康集團恢復了停工16年的柳京飯店的建造工程<ref name="doom"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mysinchew.com/node/11909 |title=Korea: N Korea Resumes Construction of Luxury Hotel |date=2008-05-25 |publisher=MySinchew |access-date=2009-07-05 |archive-date=2011-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809140809/http://www.mysinchew.com/node/11909 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。奧斯康集團此前已與北韓政府簽訂價值4億美元的協議以建設與營運北韓境內的[[3G|3G]][[蜂窝网络|蜂窝网络]]，而奧斯康集團表示其電訊業務交易與柳京飯店的工程並無直接關係。<ref name=doom/>。北韓政府官員於2008年稱柳京飯店將於2012年[[共和國永遠的主席|共和國永遠的主席]]金日成100歲冥誕時完工<ref name="Kirk2008"/>。奧斯康集團首席營運官哈立德·比沙拉於2009年稱集團在解決柳京飯店大樓的結構問題上“未遇到太多問題”，並稱柳京飯店頂部將設旋轉餐廳<ref name=doom/>。

2011年7月，有報導稱柳京飯店的外牆已完工<ref name="exterior">{{cite web |title=Photos: 'Hotel of Doom' Exterior Completed |work=The Huffington Post |date=2011-07-14 |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/07/14/north-koreas-ryugyong-hot_n_892540.html |access-date=2022-03-14 |archive-date=2016-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905073948/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/07/14/north-koreas-ryugyong-hot_n_892540.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。奧斯康集團在復工期間為柳京飯店安裝外牆玻璃面板與電訊天線<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-korea-north-hotel-idUSSEO9654020080717 |title=Lifestyle: North Korea's 'Hotel of Doom' wakes from its coma |work=Reuters |last=Herskovitz |first=Jon |date=2008-07-17 |access-date=2009-07-05 |archive-date=2021-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211225215202/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-korea-north-hotel-idUSSEO9654020080717 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|高麗旅遊|Koryo Tours}}於2012年9月首次對外公開柳京飯店內部的照片，其時柳京飯店未安裝太多固定裝置與家具<ref>{{cite web |title=North Korea's Ryugyong 'Hotel of Doom' pictures released |publisher=BBC News |date=2012-09-27 |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-19741830 |access-date=2022-03-14 |archive-date=2021-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409144133/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-19741830 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Koryo">{{cite web |url=http://koryogroup.com/blog/?p=1156 |title=Ryugyong Hotel Special Report! |website=Koryo Tours |archive-date=2014-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110072645/http://koryogroup.com/blog/?p=1156 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。

===取消計劃===
2012年11月，國際酒店營運商[[凯宾斯基酒店|凯宾斯基酒店]]宣告其將營運柳京飯店，而柳京飯店則預計於2013年中局部啓用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/11/01/north-koreas-ryugyong-hotel-will-probably-open_n_2056346.html |work=The Huffington Post |title=North Korea's Ryugyong Hotel Will 'Probably' Open Next Year, Be Managed By Kempinski |date=2012-11-01 |agency=Associated Press |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103174135/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/11/01/north-koreas-ryugyong-hotel-will-probably-open_n_2056346.html |archive-date=2012-11-03 }}</ref><ref name=bloom>{{cite news |last=Yoon |first=Sangwon |title=Kempinski to Operate World's Tallest Hotel in North Korea |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2012-11-01/north-korea-gets-world-s-tallest-hotel-as-kempinski-opens-tower |publisher=Bloomberg |date=2012-11-01 |accessdate=2022-03-14 |archive-date=2022-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217120844/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2012-11-01/north-korea-gets-world-s-tallest-hotel-as-kempinski-opens-tower |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年3月，柳京飯店啓用的計劃遭推遲<ref name="Yonhap2013">{{cite web |url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/northkorea/2013/03/29/28/0401000000AEN20130329005600315F.HTML |title=Plan to open high-rise hotel in Pyongyang suspended due to 'market conditions' |date=2013-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604073030/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/northkorea/2013/03/29/28/0401000000AEN20130329005600315F.HTML |archive-date=2013-06-04 |url-status=live |publisher=Yonhap News Agency }}</ref>。凱賓斯基酒店澄清其先前聲明的內容僅進行過“初步討論”<ref name="Strochlic2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/05/22/nobody-s-home-at-the-hermit-kingdom-s-ghost-hotel.html |title=Nobody's Home at the Hermit Kingdom's Ghost Hotel |work=The Daily Beast |date=2014-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151112011112/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/05/22/nobody-s-home-at-the-hermit-kingdom-s-ghost-hotel.html |archive-date=2015-11-12 |url-status=live |first=Nina |last=Strochlic |location=New York }}</ref>，而由於“目前無法進入市場”的關係，凱賓斯基酒店未就柳京飯店項目簽署任何協議<ref name="O’Carroll2013">{{cite web |last=O'Carroll |first=Chad |title=Kempinski Freezes 'Hotel of Doom' Plans in North Korea |work=NK News |date=2013-03-28 |url=https://www.nknews.org/2013/03/kempinski-freezes-hotel-of-doom-plans-in-north-korea/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928023653/http://www.nknews.org/2013/03/kempinski-freezes-hotel-of-doom-plans-in-north-korea/ |archive-date=2015-09-28 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

凱賓斯基未詳細説明柳京飯店延遲啓用的原因，但評論員認為[[2013年朝鲜核试验|2013年北韓核試驗]]相關的國際緊張局勢、經濟風險與施工延誤可能是延遲啓用的部分原因。<ref name="Yonhap2013"/><ref name="O’Carroll2013"/><ref name="CNN2013">{{cite web |title=Travel: North Korea's vast Ryugyong Hotel not opening yet after all |url=http://travel.cnn.com/north-korea-ryugyong-hotel-kempinski-pyongrang-open-341481 |publisher=CNN |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905225729/http://travel.cnn.com/north-korea-ryugyong-hotel-kempinski-pyongrang-open-341481 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |url-status=live |date=2013-04-25 |quote=Despite its flashy exterior, the hotel's interior showed no sign of being close to completion in December {{bracket|2012}}. }}</ref>

===完工、啓用與翻新===
有跡象表明柳京飯店於2016年末正進行翻新，並且有報導稱奧斯康集團派出代表訪-{}-問了北韓<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nknews.org/2016/12/lights-on-at-north-koreas-ryugyong-hotel-of-doom/|title=Lights on at North Korea's Ryugyong 'hotel of doom'|first=Chad|last=O'Carroll|publisher=NK News|date=2016-12-02|accessdate=2022-03-14|archive-date=2021-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211001193736/https://www.nknews.org/2016/12/lights-on-at-north-koreas-ryugyong-hotel-of-doom/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據《[[每日镜报|每日镜报]]》於2016年12月14日的報導，柳京飯店亮起燈光<ref name="completion"/>。2017年7月27日，柳京飯店正式啓用<ref name="opening"/>。

柳京飯店現場於2017年與2018年初有施工跡象，並正在修建連接道路<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/world/hotel-of-doom-takes-kims-illusion-building-sky-high-0txmm66fh|title='Hotel of Doom' takes Kim's illusion-building sky high|last=Sherwell|first=Philip|date=2017-08-06|work=The Times|access-date=2017-08-06|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507030515/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/world/hotel-of-doom-takes-kims-illusion-building-sky-high-0txmm66fh|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nknews.org/2018/02/new-roads-connected-to-pyongyangs-unfinished-ryugyong-hotel/|title=New roads connected to Pyongyang's unfinished Ryugyong Hotel|first=Chad|last=O'Carroll|publisher=NK News|date=2018-02-26|accessdate=2022-03-14|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206223918/https://www.nknews.org/2018/02/new-roads-connected-to-pyongyangs-unfinished-ryugyong-hotel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年4月的報導稱柳京飯店大樓頂部安裝了一個顯示[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國國旗|北韓國旗]]的大型LED螢幕<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nknews.org/2018/04/huge-led-display-added-to-top-of-pyongyangs-iconic-ryugyong-hotel-photos|title=Huge LED display added to top of Pyongyang's iconic Ryugyong Hotel: photo|first=Chad|last=O'Carroll|publisher=NK News|date=2018-04-02|accessdate=2022-03-14|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125235534/https://www.nknews.org/2018/04/huge-led-display-added-to-top-of-pyongyangs-iconic-ryugyong-hotel-photos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。柳京飯店大樓的一翼全翼於翌月亦安裝了LED螢幕<ref>{{cite news|last=Talmadge|first=Eric|date=2018-12-30|title=World's tallest empty hotel lit up with N. Korean propaganda|url=https://apnews.com/8e6a3919627844a58aa5cfa095515956|access-date=2019-10-31|archive-date=2021-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218000906/https://apnews.com/8e6a3919627844a58aa5cfa095515956|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且有報導稱柳京飯店大樓已預備供酒店業者進駐<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.nknews.org/2018/05/enormous-led-light-wall-added-to-side-of-pyongyangs-ryugyong-hotel |title= Enormous LED light wall added to side of Pyongyang's Ryugyong Hotel |first= Chad |last= O'Carroll |publisher= NK News |date= 2018-05-21 |accessdate= 2022-03-14 |archive-date= 2020-05-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200509171054/https://www.nknews.org/2018/05/enormous-led-light-wall-added-to-side-of-pyongyangs-ryugyong-hotel/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2018年7月時，LED螢幕用於播放動畫與電影<ref>{{cite news|url= https://www.nknews.org/2018/07/despite-sanctions-multiple-new-construction-projects-emerging-in-pyongyang|title= Despite sanctions, multiple new construction projects emerging in Pyongyang|first= Colin|last= Zwirko|publisher= NK News|date= 2018-07-20|accessdate= 2022-03-14|archive-date= 2020-11-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041226/https://www.nknews.org/2018/07/despite-sanctions-multiple-new-construction-projects-emerging-in-pyongyang/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。柳京飯店正門上方於2019年6月安裝書有酒店[[諺文|諺文]]與[[韓語羅馬字表記法|羅馬字]]名稱的新招牌<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2019/jun/27/australian-student-alek-sigley-reportedly-arrested-in-north-korea|title=Australian student reportedly arrested in North Korea out of contact since Tuesday, family say|first=Michael|last=McGowan|work=The Guardian|date=2019-06-27|accessdate=2022-03-14|archive-date=2021-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211001195732/https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2019/jun/27/australian-student-alek-sigley-reportedly-arrested-in-north-korea|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

